.SH ADVANCECOMP VERSION 1.7 2003/08 
.PD 0
.IP \(bu
Fixed a Segmentation Fault bug on the advmng \(hyr option on
the latest gcc.
.IP \(bu
Better and faster (MMX) move recognition in the advmng scroll
compression.
.IP \(bu
